description: Welcome to The Regatta in the Lake Shore East. Unit has been freshly painted, new carpets installed, and new laundry.  Tons of Natural Sunlight, this SW Corner Unit offers a split floor plan layout, with views of the Lake, Harbor, River, Lakeshore East Park and Millennium Park!  Highly upgraded; Custom Cabinets, High End Appliances, Crown Molding & Balcony. Full Amenity Building with Indoor Swimming Pool, Hot Tub, Gym, Theater Room, Game Rooms and shared outdoor Sundeck. Located blocks from the Chicago Riverwalk & the Lakefront plus surrounded by parks, this home embodies everything Chicago has to offer, with easy access to downtown, vibrant nightlife, and endless dining and entertainment options. This is city living at its finest! 1 parking space available for additional 40k.
